      "content": "therapists just want to fix me so i can go back to normal, but there is no normal anymore. it's like i'm stuck in this void. i just look at the clock and realize i have to endure another twelve hours of this feeling, and then another twelve after that. it's just an endless loop of suffering. i honestly just feel like i've reached the end of my rope... like i've run out of reasons to even try to make it to next week.",
